snippet.title: Lords of New York - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Face off against the toughest gangsters in New York on January 19th, with four-player multiplayer or against relentless AI. If you're gonna win, you've got to play dirty. See you on Steam! 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/404070/
